  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter, randomized, placebo-controlled, double-blind, Phase II study.

      The objective of this study is to evaluate the efficacy and safety of 12 weeks of treatment
      with CJC-1134-PC in patients with type 2 diabetes mellitus who are currently on metformin
      monotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
